        "content": "## Host Metrics Status\n\n**✅ Auto-running via setup script**\n\nAll metrics are being collected from `docker stats minikube` on the host machine.\n\n### Available Metrics\n\n| Metric | Description |\n|--------|-------------|\n| CPU | Container CPU usage percentage |\n| Memory | Container memory usage (bytes & %) |\n| Memory Limit | Container memory limit (bytes) |\n| Network I/O | Network RX/TX bytes |\n| Block I/O | Disk read/write bytes |\n\n### Management\n\n```bash\n# Status\nps aux | grep docker-stats\n\n# Stop\n./stop-host-metrics.sh\n\n# Restart\n./setup-host-metrics.sh\n```"
